Modifications and enhancements:
- Added technical analysis indicators (SMA, EMA, RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands, ATR, VWAP)
- Added market analysis tools and trend detection
- Added multi-symbol comparison functionality
- Enhanced security with input validation and error sanitization
- Added support for Binance Testnet
- Upgraded dependencies to fix security vulnerabilities

All modifications maintain backward compatibility with the original API.